# Navigation

# Pivot into a middle point
Mouse Middle Button
pen btn 1

# Zoom
Mouse Scroll whell
ctrl + Mouse Middle Button
ctrl + pen btn 1
Numpad +
Numpad -

# Pan
Shift + mouse middle button
Shift + pen btn 1

# Snap navigation
Click on gizmo

# Center view (zoom all)
Shift + C
Home button

# Zoom to selected object
Numpad decimal point

# Cam view
Numpad 0

# Walk mode (3D Viewport)
view > Navigation > Fly Navigation